      "Assessment": "Weakly supported"
    },
    "Drug-related eosinophilia": {
      "Support": "Peripheral eosinophilia.",
      "Against": "Does not explain CSF pleocytosis or the severity of the neurological decline.",
      "Assessment": "Unsupported"
