      "Support": "Travel history to Thailand; eating street food; CSF eosinophilia; migratory neurologic symptoms.",
      "Against": "Symptoms are relatively rapid; G. spinigerum usually presents with radicular pain but is a classic cause of eosinophilic meningitis in travelers.",
      "Assessment": "Well-supported"
    },
